\gcd(a,bc)=1
1=ax+by=au+cv
1=(ax+by)(au+cv)=a(aux+cvx+byu)+bc(yv)
 b, a(x) + b(cy) = 1 => gcd(a,b) = 1 
c, a(x) + (by)c = 1 => gcd(a,c) = 1. 
